{"tid":1236577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信投訴CCTVB嚴重違反電視通用業務守則","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:45:47.000Z","uid":12302,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8febd3ec386a0ba97d092c66bf77001c81d902e1","tid":1236577,"uid":12302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2&amp;fbclid=IwAR0qjkcz95ZsExoNn4R2aRfn1S7RgwMTspcqC61Kb4J_BcazL3azOdVK-jY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2%26fbclid%3DIwAR0qjkcz95ZsExoNn4R2aRfn1S7RgwMTspcqC61Kb4J_BcazL3azOdVK-jY&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZChX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=50474fe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2&amp;fbclid=IwAR0qjkcz95ZsExoNn4R2aRfn1S7RgwMTspcqC61Kb4J_BcazL3azOdVK-jY</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">轉載至:</span></strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/posts/2277815218971955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fposts%2F2277815218971955&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZChX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=59582eca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/posts/2277815218971955</a><br />\n歡迎大家提供template及各項修改建議"},{"pid":"73f6b00bd577fe0854c2eed98ae74dd20df8f309","tid":1236577,"uid":12302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20